Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}早上好{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Good morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在是美丽的库母茨郡的上午八点{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It's 8:00 in wonderful Coombs County,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}本地警方再一次拒绝确认或否认…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}where once again state police have refused to confirm or deny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}当地居民接连目睹的神秘“空中之光”的发现{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}more of those mysterious "lights in the sky" sightings by local residents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}以下是“漫游空中”电台记者对目击者…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Roving air reporters spoke with Miss Josie Floss,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}乔西福洛斯女士所作的采访{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}who made just such a sighting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我亲眼看见那些亮光{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I've seen those lights with my own eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}当我报警的时候，他们告诉我说那是沼气在燃烧{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}And when I called the police, they told me it was swamp gas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}简直是扯淡！库母茨郡哪儿来的沼气？{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bullshit! Ain't no swamps in Coombs County!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我跟你说，非法的外来生物将借助这光…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I tell you, with them illegal aliens...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是个好天气啊！\N{\rEng}Gonna be a sparkling day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好天气！\N{\rEng}Sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直要把我逼疯了！克莱拉！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Makes me crazy! Clara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱拉！\N{\rEng}Clara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这儿又没电了，克莱拉！\N{\rEng}My electric's gone out again, Clara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要错过我的肥皂剧了！\N{\rEng}I'm gonna miss my soaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，你别嚷嚷了！\N{\rEng}Oh, stop your yakking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比尔？\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bill?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比尔，艾尔维拉那儿又停电了\N{\rEng}Bill, Elvira's blacked out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我传个话\N{\rEng}Pass the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过得愉快，宝贝儿！\N{\rEng}Have a nice day, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢你，布恩夫人  你也一样\N{\rEng}Okay, thanks, Mrs. Boone. You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔维拉那儿又没电了\N{\rEng}{\i1}Elvira's got no electric.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看不成她的肥皂剧了  她要气炸了！\N{\rEng}She can't see her soaps, she'll hyperventilate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个野餐的好日子，玛姬！\N{\rEng}Great day for a picnic, Maggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是等不及了，布恩先生  祝你逮到条大鱼哦！\N{\rEng}Can't wait, Mr. Boone. Catch yourself a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽力而为\N{\rEng}If I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶，你的午餐做好放在冰箱里了\N{\rEng}Granny, I fixed your lunch and put it in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩得尽兴哦，孩子！\N{\rEng}Have fun, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定你一个人能行吗？\N{\rEng}Sure you're gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的，宝贝儿\N{\rEng}I'll be fine, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你管你去吧  再见！\N{\rEng}Now you just run along. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，罗根夫人\N{\rEng}Hi, Mrs. Rogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，玛姬\N{\rEng}Hi, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐盒找到了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you find that picnic basket yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在客厅里呢\N{\rEng}It's in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，谢谢  亚里克斯呢？\N{\rEng}Oh, thanks. Where's Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还能去哪儿呢？\N{\rEng}Where else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N{\rEng}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯\N{\rEng}Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，太空之子路易斯\N{\rEng}Good morning, space-son Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球人啊！\N{\rEng}Earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯\N{\rEng}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Jane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔维拉那儿又没电了\N{\rEng}Elvira's electric is out again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要是看不到她的肥皂剧又要发疯了！\N{\rEng}and she's gonna get hyper if she can't see her soaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶，告诉艾尔维拉，亚里克斯会赶在肥皂剧开始前…\N{\rEng}Granny, tell Elvira that Alex will be over
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把线路修好的\N{\rEng}to patch her electric in time for the soaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉她的，珍妮  艾尔维拉！\N{\rEng}I'll tell her, Jane. Elvira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-路易斯！ -艾尔维拉！\N{\rEng}- Louis! - Elvira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯！\N{\rEng}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去把亚里克斯叫过来\N{\rEng}Go tell Alex that I need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当心着点，外星人！\N{\rEng}Beware, aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 罗根——宇宙军学员…\N{\rEng}Louis Rogan, the cosmic cadet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太空复仇者——前来收拾你！\N{\rEng}the space avenger, is on your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You have been recruited by the Star League to defend the Frontier{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}作好准备！即将发射升空！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Get ready. Prepare for blastoff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，开始吧！\N{\rEng}Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}准备进行目标射击训练，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Prepare for target light practice, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，妈妈在找你！\N{\rEng}Mom's looking for you, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打那儿！打那儿！\N{\rEng}Right there! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准\N{\rEng}Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他们经过中点时…\N{\rEng}They're all through the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就射击，知道了吗？\N{\rEng}Shoot them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在自下向上射击\N{\rEng}Now from the bottom up, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个\N{\rEng}There's one right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行，打得不错  那里！\N{\rEng}Okay, doing good. Right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的头挪开好吧，路易斯？\N{\rEng}Move your head, will you, Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，对不起\N{\rEng}Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Maggie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，大伙儿！你们好吗？\N{\rEng}Hey, you guys. Hi. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点儿，亚里克斯  他们到了！\N{\rEng}Come on, Alex. They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬——拖车场女王！\N{\rEng}Maggie, queen of the trailer park!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星空战士亚里克斯 罗根请求…\N{\rEng}Well, Starfighter Alex Rogan requests permission
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转由我弟弟路易斯来驾驶，长官！\N{\rEng}to turn the bridge over to my little brother, Louis, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈，你们这群白痴死定了！\N{\rEng}Okay, you dorks are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被打败了  请再投入二十五美分\N{\rEng}You are defeated. 25 cents more, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，破玩意儿！\N{\rEng}Oh, crapola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-罗根，快点儿！ -嘿，亚里克斯，日子过得可好？\N{\rEng}- Rogan, come on. - Hey, Alex, how you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-稍等一下  -我们快走吧，伙计\N{\rEng}- Just a second. - Big Al. Let's do it, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快啊，亚里克斯  赶紧！\N{\rEng}Come on, Alex. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，你到底去不去？\N{\rEng}Alex, did it come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，不  我不想去了\N{\rEng}Uh, no. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了，罗根？\N{\rEng}What's it this time, Rogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要打算参军了？\N{\rEng}You joining the Foreign Legion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，长官，乡亲们  都来看看啊！\N{\rEng}Yes, sir, folks. Step right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见见我们的冒险家亚里克斯 罗根的…\N{\rEng}Meet boy adventurer Alex Rogan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走向失败的世界环游\N{\rEng}on the last leg of his worldwide tour to nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑哦，布雷克\N{\rEng}Funny, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为我在这儿就是看你们显摆汽车…\N{\rEng}You guys think I'm gonna hang out here, watch you shine your pickup,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个星期六晚上在酒店喝得烂醉，还吐得一塌糊涂…\N{\rEng}go to the drive-in, get drunk and throw up every Saturday night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还跟在别人屁股后面上大学？\N{\rEng}go to City College like everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧，伙计  我要用生命成就一番大业\N{\rEng}Forget it, man. I'm doing something with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哦！较真儿先生！  -亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}- Mr. Serioso. - Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝儿，艾尔维拉家又停电了\N{\rEng}Honey, Elvira's electric is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，妈，那要花掉我一整天\N{\rEng}Oh, Ma, that's gonna take all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还打算去银湖玩呢\N{\rEng}I was going to Silver Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝儿，我知道  真的很抱歉  我要做中饭和晚饭\N{\rEng}Honey, I know. I'm sorry. I'm working lunch and dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一天都要在镇上\N{\rEng}I'm gonna be in town all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，好吧  算了，妈，我去修吧\N{\rEng}Oh, all right. Okay, Ma. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了，宝贝儿！\N{\rEng}Thanks, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我们要迟到了{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}We're gonna be late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…你们…\N{\rEng}Look. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们去吧  我不去了\N{\rEng}You'd just better go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，亚里克斯，我留下\N{\rEng}No. Alex, I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用，没关系的  修好得要花上一段时间\N{\rEng}No. That's okay. This'll take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我修好了来找你们\N{\rEng}I'll catch up with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯…\N{\rEng}Alex...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜，罗根！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bye-bye, Rogan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿见啦，老兄！\N{\rEng}{\i1}See you, dude!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，快来帮忙啊！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex, come help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，亚里克斯，能帮我一下吗？\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hey, Alex. Could you give me a hand here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Thanks, Alex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我们今晚该做点什么呢？{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}What should we do tonight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}谁知道啊{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}打牌怎么样？{\i0}\N{\rEng}How about cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}嘿，是个好主意！{\i0}\N{\rEng}Hey, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是我们昨晚刚打过啊{\i0}\N{\rEng}But we played cards last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那…{\i0}\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}太太们今晚要进城跳舞{\i0}\N{\rEng}The missus wants to go into town tonight and go dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}鱼在水里使老大劲地向下扯{\i0}\N{\rEng}The fish were really biting down there at the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}今天钓得真尽兴{\i0}\N{\rEng}It was pleasant fishing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是啊  明天依然是个好天气{\i0}\N{\rEng}Yup. It's gonna be pleasant tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}根据农历来看，今年夏天可是个好夏天啊{\i0}\N{\rEng}Gonna be a pleasant summer according to Farmer's Almanac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是啊  我最爱农历了{\i0}\N{\rEng}Yeah. I love the Farmer's Almanac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我研究了好多年了{\i0}\N{\rEng}I've been reading it for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You have been recruited by the Star League{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}to defend the Frontier against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}作好准备！即将发射升空！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Get ready. Prepare for blastoff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}准备进行目标射击训练，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Prepare for target light practice, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，嗨，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Oh, hi, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，Otis\N{\rEng}Hey, Otis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的玛姬呢？\N{\rEng}Where's your Maggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问得好\N{\rEng}Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想…在外面玩得尽兴着呢\N{\rEng}Out having a good time, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，你从来也没玩得尽兴过\N{\rEng}Oh. And you never have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对？\N{\rEng}Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我就喜欢帮人维修用了三十年的保险丝箱\N{\rEng}Oh, sure. I love patching 30-year-old fuse panels
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还喜欢帮人通马桶\N{\rEng}and plunging people's toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otis，我从来也没有机会…\N{\rEng}Otis, I never even get a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿玩得尽兴过\N{\rEng}to have a good time around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情总是会改变的  永远都这样\N{\rEng}Things change. Always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会有机会的\N{\rEng}You'll get your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是，当它来临时…\N{\rEng}lmportant thing is, when it comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要用双手紧紧地抓住它\N{\rEng}you got to grab it with both hands and hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}敌军在三、六、七区，快速接近中{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Enemy squadrons in Sectors 3, 6, 7 closing fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，杰克\N{\rEng}Thanks, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别客气\N{\rEng}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安，玛姬  -晚安\N{\rEng}Good night, Maggie. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你会去湖边找我呢\N{\rEng}Thought you were gonna meet me at the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相同的事总是发生  我没办法脱身\N{\rEng}Same thing that always happens. I couldn't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢？\N{\rEng}Where's everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，他们去看电影了\N{\rEng}Oh, they went to a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老杰克 布雷克碰巧和你同路，啊？\N{\rEng}Old Jack Blake just happened to be going your way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军在三区出现\N{\rEng}{\i1}Enemy squadron in Sector 3.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他正好顺路回家\N{\rEng}He said it was on his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克住在镇的那头\N{\rEng}Blake lives on the other side of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Come on, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想回到你身边\N{\rEng}I wanted to get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吧？\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}打得不错，星空战士！你真行！{\i0}\N{\rEng}Good show, Starfighter! Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，看啊！\N{\rEng}Alex, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，天啊！有多少？九十万？\N{\rEng}Oh, my God. What is that? 900,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九十万！你要破纪录了！\N{\rEng}900,000! You gonna bust the record!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！嘿！大家，听好了！\N{\rEng}Hey! Hey! Listen up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯破纪录了！\N{\rEng}Alex is going for the record!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纪录？\N{\rEng}Record?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去…去看看\N{\rEng}Take... Take a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了！哦，他就要打中那架了！\N{\rEng}Got them! Oh, he's gonna get that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你行的！\N{\rEng}You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otis？\N{\rEng}Otis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otis，你在嚷嚷什么？发生什么事了？\N{\rEng}Otis, what are you yelling about? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快来啊！快！\N{\rEng}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就要破纪录了！\N{\rEng}He's going to bust the record!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！快！\N{\rEng}Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都退后！别挤到他！\N{\rEng}Everyone get back! Don't crowd him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了，快退后！\N{\rEng}I said, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，你以前从来没打出过这个成绩！\N{\rEng}Alex, you never got this far before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Go, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真争气！\N{\rEng}Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯-旦指挥舰进入射程\N{\rEng}{\i1}Ko-Dan command ship entering kill zone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥舰！\N{\rEng}Command ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，是指挥舰！\N{\rEng}Oh, command ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥舰是什么？\N{\rEng}What's a command ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你行的，亚里克斯！你绝对行！\N{\rEng}You can do it, Alex! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次！加油啊！就是它！\N{\rEng}One more now. Come on! That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打的就是它！\N{\rEng}That's the one we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！太棒了！\N{\rEng}Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}晚安  你真行，亚里克斯！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Good night. Way to go, Alex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}晚安，孩子们{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Good night, kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，你真够可以的\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex, you're something else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你真棒，孩子{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You're wonderful, boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我说的话准能成真{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}If I said it once, I said it a thousand times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那孩子见得了世面{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That boy's gonna go places.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}他真够聪明的{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That's one smart boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Good night, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“晚安，亚里克斯”？等等\N{\rEng}"Good night, Alex"? Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}玛姬？玛姬？{\i0}\N{\rEng}Maggie? Maggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}等一下  你要去哪里？{\i0}\N{\rEng}Hold on a second. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\rEng}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我突然才发觉…\N{\rEng}Well, I guess it just hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要离开这儿了，对吗？\N{\rEng}You really are leaving here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，我当然要走  我们一起离开这里\N{\rEng}Of course, I'm leaving. We're both gonna leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们一起，亚里克斯？  -是啊\N{\rEng}Both of us, Alex? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对此已经谈过了\N{\rEng}We talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我入了学，我就会找个地方…\N{\rEng}When I get to school, I'm gonna find a place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后回来接你\N{\rEng}and I'm gonna come back and get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…奶奶怎么办？\N{\rEng}Well, what about Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶？\N{\rEng}Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是你自己害怕离开这个拖车场吧？\N{\rEng}Truth is, you're scared of leaving this trailer park.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不怕离开这个拖车场呢，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}I'm not scared of leaving this trailer park, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，听好\N{\rEng}Hey. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么，我都和你在一起，对吧？\N{\rEng}Whatever happens, it's you and me forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很爱你，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}I love you so much, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也永远爱你，玛姬\N{\rEng}I'll always love you, Maggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真恶心\N{\rEng}Diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬！玛姬！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Maggie! Maggie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，我要回去了  晚安\N{\rEng}Alex, I got to go in. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\rEng}Good night. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天他们会说：“一切就是从这开始的”\N{\rEng}Someday they're gonna say, "This is where it all began."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，我终于打破了“星空战士”的纪录\N{\rEng}Mom, I finally broke the Starfighter record.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，那太好了，宝贝儿\N{\rEng}Oh, that's nice, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好？简直是令人惊叹！\N{\rEng}Nice? It's stupendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Uh, Alex,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布兰纳先生知道你想尽快看到这个…\N{\rEng}Mr. Brenner knew that you'd want to see this as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他把这个带到了餐馆…\N{\rEng}so he brought it by the diner and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很兴奋，所以就把它打开了\N{\rEng}Well, I was so excited, I opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，没关系  里面说什么？\N{\rEng}Oh, that's okay. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于你的贷款\N{\rEng}It's about your loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然可以和你的朋友一起上大学\N{\rEng}You can still go to City College with your friends.
