Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商店已经关门了，先生\N{\rEng}Store's closed, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来买香烟或者泡泡糖的，孩子\N{\rEng}I'm not here for cigarettes or bubble gum, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能告诉我…\N{\rEng}Can you tell me the name of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打破那边那个游戏纪录的人的名字？\N{\rEng}who broke the record on that game over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里可以找到他？\N{\rEng}Where I might find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚里克斯 罗根  他现在就在你面前\N{\rEng}Alex Rogan. You're looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯 罗根  啊哈！\N{\rEng}Alex Rogan. Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是谁？  -森特利是我的名字\N{\rEng}Who are you? Centauri's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个游戏是我发明的  它就是我来这儿的原因\N{\rEng}I invented Starfighter, which is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的？  -当然\N{\rEng}It is? It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈一件极重要的事\N{\rEng}We have to talk about a matter of utmost importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进入我的办公室\N{\rEng}Step into my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是它  进来吧\N{\rEng}That's it. Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好怕的\N{\rEng}Nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，对了  和我的助手贝塔打个招呼\N{\rEng}Oh, yes. Say hello to my assistant, Beta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\rEng}Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗷！\N{\rEng}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须就你的精彩表现恭喜你，我的孩子\N{\rEng}I must congratulate you on your virtuoso performance, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给森特利留下了深刻的印象\N{\rEng}Centauri is impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我见过有人来，也见过有人去…\N{\rEng}I've seen them come and I've seen them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是最棒的，我的孩子  漂亮！\N{\rEng}But you're the best, my boy. Dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比其他人好十万八千里\N{\rEng}Light years ahead of the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么森特利要来这儿\N{\rEng}Which is why Centauri is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有点事来找你\N{\rEng}He's got a little proposition for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有兴趣吗？\N{\rEng}Are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧\N{\rEng}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！\N{\rEng}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\N{\rEng}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利想要给你一个惊喜\N{\rEng}Centauri wants to keep it for a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我，你会喜欢它的  一定会的！\N{\rEng}Trust me. Oh, you're gonna love it. Love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好笑的是，这一切都是出于一个错误\N{\rEng}The amusing thing about this, it's all a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个游戏…\N{\rEng}That particular Starfighter game
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该被运往维加斯的\N{\rEng}was supposed to be delivered to Vegas,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是你们那个在野草和虫子堆里的…\N{\rEng}not some flea-speck trailer park
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芝麻大小的拖车场\N{\rEng}in the middle of tumbleweeds and tarantulas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，一定是宿命，命运——误打误撞地…\N{\rEng}So, it must be fate, destiny, blind chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可以说是运气——把我们带到一起\N{\rEng}luck, even, that brings us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有首诗说得好：“往事如烟”\N{\rEng}And as the poet says, "The rest is history."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿？为什么要带我去？\N{\rEng}Where are you going? Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你了，我要给你一个惊喜\N{\rEng}I told you. I wanna save it for a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:22:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你是不是那种急着先读谜底的孩子？\N{\rEng}Hey. Are you the kind of kid who reads the last page of a mystery first?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些缠着魔术师追问奥秘的孩子？\N{\rEng}Who pesters the magician to tell you his tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些悄悄溜下楼偷看圣诞礼物的孩子？\N{\rEng}Who sneaks downstairs to peek at his Christmas presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你当然不是那样的！\N{\rEng}No. Of course you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我先不告诉你\N{\rEng}That's why I'm not gonna tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，天啊\N{\rEng}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外，我最喜欢惊喜了  难道你不是吗？\N{\rEng}Besides, I just love surprises, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！看好了！\N{\rEng}Hey, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-停车！  -天啊！\N{\rEng}Stop! Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快踩刹车！嘿…\N{\rEng}Hit the brakes! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哥伦比亚星切换为星球驱动模式\N{\rEng}{\i1}Shifting into star drive at Columba Zeta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hold tight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  嘿，让我出去！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hey. Hey, let me out of here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该有一个完全符合逻辑的理由来解释这一切\N{\rEng}There's a perfectly logical explanation for all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.99,0:26:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！等等！你要去哪儿？\N{\rEng}Hey! Wait! Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.72,0:26:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！你好  这是什么？\N{\rEng}Hi! How are you? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.82,0:26:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，你会说英语吗？我…\N{\rEng}Listen. Do you speak English? I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.79,0:26:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很不错，可是…\N{\rEng}This is nice but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.75,0:27:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利，这里发生什么情况？\N{\rEng}Centauri, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.52,0:27:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说你能来这儿他很高兴…\N{\rEng}He's just saying how delighted he is that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.79,0:27:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，如果你有什么需要能让你在这儿过得愉快…\N{\rEng}And if there's anything he can do
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.99,0:27:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他打个电话就行\N{\rEng}to make your stay more enjoyable, just give him a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.99,0:27:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿？你在说些什么？我们在哪儿？\N{\rEng}My stay? What are you talking about? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.36,0:27:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到赖罗斯星，我的孩子！\N{\rEng}Welcome to Rylos, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.50,0:27:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赖罗斯？\N{\rEng}Rylos?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.30,0:27:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你的意思是说…就像在游戏里一样？\N{\rEng}Wait a minute. You mean... You mean like in a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，他反应很快嘛  很快，是很快\N{\rEng}Oh, he's quick. He's quick. He's very quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.74,0:27:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他瞠目结舌了！再见了，亚里克斯！尽兴哦！\N{\rEng}He's speechless. So long, Alex! Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.94,0:27:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿古鲁七柱的好运永远伴你左右\N{\rEng}May the luck of the Seven Pillars of Gulu be with you at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.35,0:27:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，总有一天这些混蛋们会感谢森特利的  相信我吧\N{\rEng}Oh, someday these cheapskates will thank Centauri. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.66,0:27:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六月份的到哪儿去了？\N{\rEng}Where the hell is June?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.80,0:27:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹兰达，小甜心！\N{\rEng}Yolanda, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.79,0:28:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，玛姬\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hi, Maggs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.13,0:28:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，路易斯\N{\rEng}Hi, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.33,0:28:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他起床了吗？\N{\rEng}Is he up?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他嘟哝了一个晚上，没睡过\N{\rEng}Yeah. He's been up all night moaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.41,0:28:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.78,0:28:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈告诉我贷款的事了\N{\rEng}Your mother told me about the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么我帮得上的吗？\N{\rEng}Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，如果你需要帮忙，我就在隔壁，好吧？\N{\rEng}Listen. I'll be next door if you need anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.77,0:29:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚星群\N{\rEng}Gunstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.01,0:30:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是在做梦\N{\rEng}I got to be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.69,0:30:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，没错\N{\rEng}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.63,0:30:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，这里有个大错\N{\rEng}Listen, there's been a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.07,0:30:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况报告后立即\N{\rEng}{\i1}...immediately after situation report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.03,0:30:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导航\N{\rEng}{\i1}Navigation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.20,0:30:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到星空战士指挥部\N{\rEng}Welcome to Starfighter Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.64,0:30:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说英语了？\N{\rEng}You speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.77,0:30:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你听到的是英语  这要多亏了你的翻译装置\N{\rEng}No. You hear English, thanks to your translator device.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.58,0:30:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧，我们时间不多了\N{\rEng}Hurry up. We haven't got much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.25,0:30:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部署会议马上要开始了\N{\rEng}The briefing begins immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.82,0:30:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请和其他录取者一同前往\N{\rEng}Join the other recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.56,0:30:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！等等！\N{\rEng}Wait a minute! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.59,0:30:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！你说的录取者是什么意思？\N{\rEng}Wait a minute! What are you talking about, recruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.80,0:30:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我简直不能相信！\N{\rEng}I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.70,0:30:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意  请注意！恩德伦大使已经到达\N{\rEng}{\i1}Attention. Attention, please. Ambassador Enduran has arrived{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.01,0:30:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并将立即开始部署星空战士指挥部的人事工作\N{\rEng}{\i1}and will now address Starfighter Command personnel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.26,0:31:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,众所周知，我们绝望地探寻了很久…\N{\rEng}{\i1}As you all know, we have been on a desperate quest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.23,0:31:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉\N{\rEng}{\i1}Excuse me. Excuse me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.06,0:31:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…找到你们这些星空战士和领航员\N{\rEng}{\i1}...to find Starfighters and navigators.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.17,0:31:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我真应该把你捏得粉碎！\N{\rEng}I should... I should crush you to gorun dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.47,0:31:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我是不小心的…\N{\rEng}I'm sorry... It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.34,0:31:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要故意踩你的…\N{\rEng}I didn't mean to step on your...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.68,0:31:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道叫它什么东西\N{\rEng}Whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的生物\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hideous creature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.28,0:31:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我继续\N{\rEng}{\i1}If I may continue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.72,0:31:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的军队已经…\N{\rEng}{\i1}Our forces have...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.33,0:31:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别惹伯嘉地\N{\rEng}You don't trifle with a Bogati.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.90,0:31:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很好战\N{\rEng}They love to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.40,0:31:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们很适合打这场战争\N{\rEng}That's why they're perfect for this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是说了“战争”？\N{\rEng}Did you say "war"?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错！\N{\rEng}But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.77,0:31:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然你认为你在这儿干什么？\N{\rEng}Why else do you think you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境”\N{\rEng}You were recruited by the Star League to defend...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.17,0:31:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵”\N{\rEng}"...to defend the Frontier against Xur and the Ko-Dan Armada."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.31,0:31:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前，我们的祖先建造了这伟大的边境\N{\rEng}Eons ago, our ancestors created our great Frontier,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.85,0:31:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它对敌人来说是一道屏障\N{\rEng}a barrier of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.20,0:31:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维持着和平的宇宙体系\N{\rEng}encircling the peaceful systems of the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.07,0:32:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将潜在的灾祸拒于千里之外\N{\rEng}and forever shutting out the scourge that lurks beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.51,0:32:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙，由于无耻的背叛…\N{\rEng}Fellow Rylans, because of a dark betrayal,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.15,0:32:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的边境即将瓦解\N{\rEng}our Frontier will soon collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.82,0:32:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我们向你们——星空战士以及你们的领航员们——求助…\N{\rEng}So we turn to you, Starfighters and your navigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.02,0:32:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表着星际联盟几十亿的生命\N{\rEng}For of all the billions of creatures in the Star League,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.74,0:32:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你们几个才被证明有那…\N{\rEng}only you few were found to possess the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.38,0:32:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天赋\N{\rEng}gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.05,0:32:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你，还有你…\N{\rEng}You, and you alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.22,0:32:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正站在我们与黑暗势力的中间\N{\rEng}stand between us and the black terror of the Ko-Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.09,0:32:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.86,0:32:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Victory or death! Victory or death!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death! Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.86,0:32:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death! Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.78,0:32:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death! Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.51,0:32:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death! Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.38,0:33:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death! Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.39,0:33:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！\N{\rEng}Victory or death! Victory or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.02,0:33:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在，星空战士们，在你们的座位底下…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Now, Starfighters, if you will reach underneath your seats,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.16,0:33:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你们会发现一个装有一只手的包…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}you will find a packet which contains one hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.50,0:33:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是限制区域，对你们…\N{\rEng}This is a restricted area, off-limits to...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.32,0:33:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起，星空战士\N{\rEng}My apologies, Starfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.35,0:33:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星际导航员兼一等兵听从您指挥，长官！\N{\rEng}Star Navigator First Class Grig at your service, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.32,0:33:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，我是亚里克斯 罗根，我在家里玩这个游戏…\N{\rEng}Hi. I'm Alex Rogan. I was playing this game back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.79,0:33:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来有个人找到我…\N{\rEng}and this guy came up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.00,0:33:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他不是个人，他是外星人，对吧？\N{\rEng}Only he's not a guy. He's an alien, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.93,0:33:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我坐上他的车——只不过那不是辆车——而是艘宇宙飞船\N{\rEng}And I get into his car. Only it's not a car. It's a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.73,0:33:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里面有个大错误\N{\rEng}And, there's been a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.24,0:33:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是要这样理解…\N{\rEng}Am I to understand you're actually declining
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.21,0:33:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拒绝做一名光荣的星空战士？\N{\rEng}the honor of becoming a Starfighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.58,0:33:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEng}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了！\N{\rEng}Extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来，所有的生物都梦想成为星空战士\N{\rEng}For eons, all creatures have dreamt of being Starfighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.66,0:33:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你从哪儿来？  -地球\N{\rEng}Where you from? Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.70,0:33:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们其实和谁都没在打仗，只是互相在打\N{\rEng}And we're not at war with anybody, except each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.97,0:34:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球？地球可不是星际联盟的正式成员啊…\N{\rEng}Earth? Earth isn't a formal member of the Star League,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.74,0:34:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有等到它成熟以后我们才可以接近\N{\rEng}and isn't due to be approached until it matures.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.10,0:34:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太没规矩了\N{\rEng}This is all highly irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.04,0:34:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，是谁征用你的？\N{\rEng}Tell me. Who recruited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.44,0:34:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利\N{\rEng}Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.41,0:34:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他来了  就是他！\N{\rEng}There he is. That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.56,0:34:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利  我也许认识他\N{\rEng}Centauri. I might have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.63,0:34:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又在故伎重演了，对吧，森特利？\N{\rEng}Up to your old Excalibur tricks again, eh, Centauri?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.10,0:34:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不知道…\N{\rEng}Did it ever occur to you that it is against the law
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.47,0:34:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从星际联盟以外的地方征兵是非法的？\N{\rEng}to recruit from worlds outside the Star League?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.77,0:34:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球也受到了威胁，不是吗？\N{\rEng}Earth's in danger, too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.01,0:34:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我可没有动用神剑测试哦\N{\rEng}And, no, I did not use the Excalibur test.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.18,0:34:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只用了一个叫作“电子游戏”的东西\N{\rEng}It was called a video game.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什么关系呢？\N{\rEng}What's all the brouhaha?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.51,0:34:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之，他没有那种天赋\N{\rEng}After all, he does have the gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.38,0:34:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也许会让你很吃惊…\N{\rEng}This may come as a bit of a shock to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.86,0:34:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他并不想成为星空战士\N{\rEng}but he doesn't want to be a Starfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.93,0:34:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想成为一个…你是个懦夫吗？\N{\rEng}Doesn't want to be a... Are you a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.14,0:34:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗？\N{\rEng}Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.20,0:34:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没告诉过我！\N{\rEng}You didn't tell me about any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.51,0:34:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还钱吧，森特利！\N{\rEng}Return the money, Centauri!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.57,0:34:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还钱？你老糊涂了吗？\N{\rEng}Return the money? Are you delirious?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.91,0:35:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我花了多久发明那游戏…\N{\rEng}Do you know how long it took to invent the games,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.98,0:35:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行推广…\N{\rEng}to merchandise them,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.18,0:35:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在圣诞节前放在店里销售？\N{\rEng}to get them into the stores by Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.52,0:35:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对于你来说一定不容易…\N{\rEng}It must be terribly embarrassing for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.59,0:35:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很同情，可是…\N{\rEng}and I do sympathize. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.59,0:35:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看到他战斗了！\N{\rEng}But I saw him fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.16,0:35:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可以成为有史以来最棒的星空战士！\N{\rEng}He could be the greatest Starfighter ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.00,0:35:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是个游戏啊，森特利\N{\rEng}That was a game, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.84,0:35:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏？\N{\rEng}A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为它只是个游戏，但它也是种考验\N{\rEng}You may have thought it was a game, but it was also a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.18,0:35:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈！一种考验！\N{\rEng}Aha! A test!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.94,0:35:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它被发向宇宙，寻找那些具有天赋的人成为星空战士\N{\rEng}Sent out across the universe to find those with the gift to be Starfighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.51,0:35:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就在这儿了，我的孩子！\N{\rEng}And here you are, my boy. Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.52,0:35:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我是在这儿了  等着被杀！\N{\rEng}Right! Here I am, about to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.29,0:35:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被杀…\N{\rEng}Killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.06,0:35:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会以为它很危险吧？\N{\rEng}You don't seriously think it's dangerous, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.46,0:35:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了，相信我吧！\N{\rEng}Don't be silly! Trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.16,0:35:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔！\N{\rEng}Xur!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.09,0:36:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔！\N{\rEng}Xur!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.39,0:36:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔？\N{\rEng}Xur?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.20,0:36:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，父亲，你那强大的边境现在正在削弱\N{\rEng}Yes, Father, your mighty Frontier grows weaker by the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.38,0:36:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我父亲！\N{\rEng}Do not call me father!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.05,0:36:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有你这个儿子！\N{\rEng}You are no longer my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.52,0:36:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被我遗弃，为什么还回来？\N{\rEng}You're an outcast! Why have you returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.26,0:36:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了所有赖仑星人好，我回来了\N{\rEng}I have returned for the good of all Rylans.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.26,0:36:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带着柯-旦战舰回来？\N{\rEng}With an armada of Ko-Dan warships behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.73,0:36:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些赖仑星人会欢迎我的，父亲\N{\rEng}There are some Rylans who would welcome me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.37,0:36:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星球联盟的正义容不得你这邪教！\N{\rEng}Star League justice put down your Xurian cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.27,0:36:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的追随者既少又分散\N{\rEng}Your followers are few and scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星际联盟？\N{\rEng}Star League?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.92,0:36:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是个弱小世界的避难所，根本无法与我们匹敌！\N{\rEng}A refuge for weak worlds not worthy to be our equals!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.49,0:36:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是由赖仑星人来作决定\N{\rEng}That is for the Rylans to decide,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.02,0:36:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是由像你自己一样的一个既危险又邪恶的孩子来决定！\N{\rEng}and not for a dangerous and evil child such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.70,0:36:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而，也就是这个孩子，捕获了你的主要间谍\N{\rEng}And yet, it is this child who caught your master spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.04,0:37:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我的吧，赖仑星人！\N{\rEng}Hear me, Rylans!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.58,0:37:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当戈兰星的绿月黯然失色的时候，柯-旦的军队将会入侵\N{\rEng}When the green moon of Galan is eclipsed, Ko-Dan Armada will invade,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.56,0:37:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们强大的星空战士也救不了你们\N{\rEng}and not even your mighty Starfighters will be able to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.30,0:37:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走着瞧，祖尔  我们走着瞧！\N{\rEng}We shall see, Xur. We shall see!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.68,0:37:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然想走吗？\N{\rEng}You still want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.35,0:38:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想错过这里的精彩？\N{\rEng}And miss all the excitement?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.87,0:38:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小屁孩儿\N{\rEng}Little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.07,0:38:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发明了游戏，找到了那个孩子，带他过去…\N{\rEng}I invent the game, find the kid, drag him up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.47,0:38:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然不想成为星空战士\N{\rEng}and he doesn't want to be a Starfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.97,0:38:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也算放弃了！\N{\rEng}I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.89,0:38:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制中心，你能从停车角度复制我们的星角差吗？\N{\rEng}{\i1}Control, do you copy our star angle difference from parking angle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.16,0:39:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,δβ2-6，δγ3-5\N{\rEng}{\i1}Delta beta two at six, delta gamma three at five.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.35,0:39:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔王命令我把他的权杖拿来\N{\rEng}Emperor Xur ordered me to bring his scepter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.39,0:39:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他进来\N{\rEng}Let him enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.09,0:39:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标位置仍可见\N{\rEng}{\i1}Target vector remains on scope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.25,0:39:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你们柯-旦王的一样，对吧，克里尔指挥长？\N{\rEng}Just like your Ko-Dan emperor's, isn't it, Commander Kril?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.79,0:39:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要统治，单单靠权杖是办不到的，祖尔\N{\rEng}It takes more than a scepter to rule, Xur, even on Rylos.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.76,0:39:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得没错，克里尔\N{\rEng}You're right, Kril.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单靠权杖的确办不到\N{\rEng}It does take more than a scepter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:40:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们忍这个蠢货要忍多久？\N{\rEng}How long must we endure this fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.02,0:40:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边境出现情况\N{\rEng}We have a break in the Frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.96,0:40:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射流星弹！\N{\rEng}Fire the meteor gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.33,0:40:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲爱的柯-旦朋友！惟恐我们忘记…\N{\rEng}My dear Ko-Dan friends! Lest we forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.57,0:40:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的王委任我担任本军的指挥\N{\rEng}it was your own emperor who granted me command of this Armada.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.50,0:40:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有我才知道通往边境的路\N{\rEng}For only I hold the secret to the Frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.17,0:40:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只有我才知道星空战士基地\N{\rEng}Only I know the location of the Starfighter base.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.91,0:40:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此，只有我才有权命令开火！\N{\rEng}And therefore, only I will give the order to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.93,0:40:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我，祖尔\N{\rEng}Forgive me, Xur.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.24,0:40:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原谅你，克里尔指挥长\N{\rEng}You are forgiven, Commander Kril.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.24,0:40:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流星弹…发射！\N{\rEng}Meteor gunner...fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.76,0:41:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中士！\N{\rEng}Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.50,0:41:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十一区有不明飞行物侵入，长官\N{\rEng}I have an unidentified incoming object in Sector 31 , sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.44,0:41:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们的目标是基地！警戒状态！\N{\rEng}They're headed for the base! Alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.18,0:41:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们受到攻击！\N{\rEng}We are under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.45,0:41:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍，我们受到攻击！\N{\rEng}I repeat, we are under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开启自动排斥枪！\N{\rEng}Activate automatic repulser guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.46,0:42:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警戒状态！警戒状态！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Condition Red! Condition Red!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.65,0:42:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于成功了！\N{\rEng}At last, it is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.12,0:42:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久，边境将瓦解…\N{\rEng}Soon the Frontier will be down
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.49,0:42:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也将向他们的新帝王俯首称臣！\N{\rEng}and they will bow to their new emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.76,0:42:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则，我就用他们的灰烬抹灰天空！\N{\rEng}Or I will darken the sky with their ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.46,0:43:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥长，祖尔的间谍报告说…\N{\rEng}Commander, the Xurian spy reports
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.43,0:43:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个星空战士逃跑了\N{\rEng}that one Starfighter has escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.27,0:43:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑？\N{\rEng}Escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.59,0:43:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定不需要我帮忙？\N{\rEng}You sure I can't give you a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.89,0:43:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经帮得够多的了  谢谢\N{\rEng}You've done quite enough already. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.03,0:43:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.00,0:43:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就几公里远了，我想……\N{\rEng}It's only a few more miles from here. I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.00,0:43:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我就走回去吧\N{\rEng}I guess I can walk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.07,0:43:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期！再见，森特利！\N{\rEng}So long! Bye, Centauri!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Oh, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.23,0:43:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你！\N{\rEng}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.80,0:43:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，听着  我不能拿你的礼物，森特利\N{\rEng}Hey, listen. I can't take a present from you, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.14,0:43:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把我变得倾家荡产…\N{\rEng}He reduces me to poverty again
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.51,0:44:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还认为我是给他礼物！\N{\rEng}and he thinks I'm giving him a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.17,0:44:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么世道啊？\N{\rEng}What a world this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.54,0:44:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那它是什么？\N{\rEng}What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.88,0:44:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是另一次机会，我的孩子！\N{\rEng}It's a second chance, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.88,0:44:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你改变了主意，按下通讯按钮就可以了\N{\rEng}If you change your mind, just tap the communo-crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.83,0:44:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你留着它吧  -亚里克斯，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Keep it. Alex, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.37,0:44:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你正在背离历史  历史！\N{\rEng}You're walking away from history. History!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.37,0:44:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥伦布说过他想呆在家里吗？没有！\N{\rEng}Did Chris Columbus say he wanted to stay home? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.94,0:44:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是赖特兄弟认为只有鸟儿才会飞翔会怎么样呢？\N{\rEng}What if the Wright Brothers thought that only birds should fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.64,0:44:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉罗卡有没有认为尤鲁士人丑得无药可救呢？\N{\rEng}And did Geloca think the Yulus were too ugly to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.51,0:44:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是吉罗卡？\N{\rEng}Who's Geloca?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.85,0:44:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管了\N{\rEng}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.85,0:44:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，森特利  我不是他们中的任何一个\N{\rEng}Listen, Centauri. I'm not any of those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.22,0:44:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一个来自拖车场的孩子\N{\rEng}I'm a kid from a trailer park.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.79,0:44:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真是那样想的话，那你也就这样了！\N{\rEng}If that's what you think, then that's all you'll ever be!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.18,0:45:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，玛姬！\N{\rEng}Hey, Maggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.41,0:45:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快听听，你绝不会相信的\N{\rEng}Listen to this. You're not going to believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.25,0:45:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}I told you, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.42,0:45:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我的…你是怎么说的来着？\N{\rEng}Me and my... How did you put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.55,0:45:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“奇怪的性冲动”再也不会和你说话了！\N{\rEng}"Strange sexual urges," aren't talking to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.84,0:46:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁？\N{\rEng}Who's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.97,0:46:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘！你会把路易斯吵醒的\N{\rEng}Shh! You're gonna wake up Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.13,0:46:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！你看上去就和我一样！\N{\rEng}Hey, you look like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.10,0:46:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，我是你的替身\N{\rEng}Of course I do. I'm the beta unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.97,0:46:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替身是什么玩意儿？\N{\rEng}What the hell's a beta unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.47,0:46:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替身是一个模拟体，一个你的完全的复制体，只是嗓门没那么大\N{\rEng}A beta unit is a simuloid, an exact duplicate of you, only not as loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.01,0:46:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？\N{\rEng}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.14,0:46:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在汽车里，不记得了？\N{\rEng}I was in the starcar, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.48,0:46:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们握过手？\N{\rEng}We shook hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.81,0:46:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不幸的是，我成了你\N{\rEng}I became you, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.03,0:46:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说白了，你就是个机器人？\N{\rEng}Let me get this straight. You're a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.56,0:46:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？\N{\rEng}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.30,0:46:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个既有艺术性，又是行业内顶尖级的替身……\N{\rEng}I'm a state-of-the-art, top-of-the-line beta unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.10,0:46:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被放到这儿，当你不在的时候顶替你\N{\rEng}put here as a courtesy replacement for while you're away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.84,0:46:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还真幸运啊\N{\rEng}Lucky me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.71,0:46:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，你怎么回来了？\N{\rEng}Wait a minute. What are you doing back?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.64,0:46:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么玩笑？那里在打仗！\N{\rEng}Are you kidding? It's war up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.41,0:47:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，拯救鲸鱼却不拯救整个宇宙，啊？\N{\rEng}Oh. Save the whales and not the universe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.22,0:47:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不去打仗？\N{\rEng}Well, why don't you go up there and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.15,0:47:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模拟体不能打仗  这是不允许的\N{\rEng}Simuloids can't fight. We're not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.76,0:47:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那告诉他们你就是我  假装嘛！\N{\rEng}Well, tell them that you're me! Pretend!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.30,0:47:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静点，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Be quiet, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.80,0:47:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，路易斯\N{\rEng}Sorry, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.57,0:47:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的礼物！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Thanks for the lift!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.94,0:47:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别客气，伙计  再见！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Sure thing, buddy. See you around!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.97,0:47:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.91,0:47:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已被星空联盟录取\N{\rEng}{\i1}You have been recruited by the Star League{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.34,0:47:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誓死保卫边境…\N{\rEng}{\i1}to defend the Frontier against Yur and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.48,0:48:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…嘿！你对玛姬做了什么？\N{\rEng}And, hey, what did you do to Maggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.05,0:48:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对她？\N{\rEng}Do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.55,0:48:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们坐在外面，看着星空…\N{\rEng}We're sitting outside, looking at the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.05,0:48:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把舌头伸到我耳朵里来\N{\rEng}and she sticks her tongue in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.82,0:48:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尖叫起来  我明天道歉总好了吧？\N{\rEng}I screamed. I'll apologize tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.69,0:48:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该在这儿的！\N{\rEng}You're not gonna be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.19,0:48:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就得和森特利一起回去！\N{\rEng}You're going back with Centauri right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.33,0:48:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}What's up, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.43,0:48:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去睡觉，路易斯  不然我就告诉妈妈你和你那些《花花公子》的事\N{\rEng}Back to sleep, Louis, or I'm telling Ma about your Playboys.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.87,0:48:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把事情搞砸了，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}You're blowing it, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.31,0:48:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事！\N{\rEng}What the shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了快回去睡觉，路易斯  不然我就告诉妈妈你和你那些《花花公子》的事\N{\rEng}I said, back to sleep, Louis, or I'm telling Ma about your Playboys!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.39,0:48:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，森特利\N{\rEng}Come in, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.09,0:48:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，快回来\N{\rEng}Come on. Get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.16,0:48:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的仿真玩具带走\N{\rEng}And take your Tonka toy with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.79,0:48:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.63,0:48:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You have been recruited by the Star League to defend the Frontier{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.64,0:48:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.42,0:48:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你已被星空联盟录取…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You have been recruited by the Star League{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.88,0:49:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}誓死保卫边境…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}to defend the Frontier against Yur...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.02,0:49:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿？出来啊？你在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where are you? Come on, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.66,0:49:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利？\N{\rEng}Centauri?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.96,0:49:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.07,0:49:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利？\N{\rEng}Centauri?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.52,0:50:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，不好！\N{\rEng}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.05,0:50:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊，亚里克斯，别那么懦弱！\N{\rEng}Come on, Alex. Don't be such a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.61,0:50:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利，当心！\N{\rEng}Centauri, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.81,0:50:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…\N{\rEng}What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.09,0:51:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏、恶臭的生物\N{\rEng}Foul stench. Dirty creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.46,0:51:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Get a good look, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.16,0:51:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢打赌你以后会看见更多\N{\rEng}You can bet your asteroids you'll be seeing more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.41,0:51:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.68,0:51:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是赞多-赞\N{\rEng}This is a Zando-Zan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.48,0:51:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种星际怪物，祖尔的走狗\N{\rEng}An interstellar hitbeast, compliments of Xur.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.22,0:51:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔？他为什么要跟踪我？\N{\rEng}Xur? Why is he after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.69,0:51:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么，他发现你是一个星空战士\N{\rEng}Somehow he found out you're a Starfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.02,0:51:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，你看，亚里克斯，你得回去  你别无选择\N{\rEng}{\i1}So you see, Alex, you got to go back. You got no choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.72,0:51:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是呆在这里的话，你就变成它们的事物了\N{\rEng}{\i1}'Cause if you stay down here, you're dog food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.69,0:51:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信森特利，我的孩子\N{\rEng}Trust Centauri, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.43,0:51:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为两小时以后，这个地方将爬满十只赞多-赞s…\N{\rEng}Because in two hours, this place will be crawling with 10 Zando-Zans
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.70,0:51:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们那木鱼脑子里只有一个目的…\N{\rEng}with just one thought on their microscopic little minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.70,0:51:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死亚里克斯罗根\N{\rEng}kill Alex Rogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.38,0:51:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死亚里克斯罗根\N{\rEng}Kill Alex Rogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.02,0:51:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说得没错，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}{\i1}He's right, Alex.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.52,0:51:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在那里你还有机会在刚星里面战斗\N{\rEng}At least up there you'll have a fighting chance in a Gunstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.25,0:51:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEng}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.42,0:52:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时，在这儿，他们会追杀替身\N{\rEng}Meanwhile, down here, they'll be going after Beta.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.49,0:52:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-替身  -替身？\N{\rEng}Beta. Beta?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.09,0:52:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  不然你以为他是干什么来的？\N{\rEng}Of course. What do you think he's here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.10,0:52:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等，森特利\N{\rEng}Wait a... Wait a second here, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.96,0:52:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，当心！\N{\rEng}Alex, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.11,0:52:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利！\N{\rEng}Centauri!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.82,0:52:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替身，去叫医生！\N{\rEng}Beta, get a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.95,0:52:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，这里看不好的，因为没有巫医\N{\rEng}No. No native cures. No witch doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.82,0:52:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事，只是擦伤\N{\rEng}I'm fine. Just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.10,0:52:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对现实吧，亚里克斯  你天生就是个星空战士\N{\rEng}Now face it, Alex. You're a born Starfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.17,0:52:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我去吗？\N{\rEng}Are you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.46,0:52:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，我们走，森特利\N{\rEng}Okay, let's go, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.79,0:52:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Good luck, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.40,0:52:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}You, too, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.40,0:53:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利呼叫星空战士指挥部\N{\rEng}Centauri to Starfighter Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.30,0:53:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利呼叫星空战士指挥部\N{\rEng}Centauri to Starfighter Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.24,0:53:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回答\N{\rEng}Come in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.60,0:53:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，森特利\N{\rEng}Hey, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.20,0:53:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所有人员注意{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Attention all personnel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.07,0:53:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}星际汽车正在接近十二号停靠点{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Starcar is approaching Docking Bay 12.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.64,0:53:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利！森特利！\N{\rEng}Centauri! Centauri!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.08,0:54:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！快踩刹车！\N{\rEng}Hey, hit the brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.56,0:54:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-格里格！嘿，格里格！  -亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Grig! Hey, Grig! Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.59,0:54:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们击中了森特利  他受伤了\N{\rEng}They got Centauri. He's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.61,0:54:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这儿\N{\rEng}He's right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.99,0:54:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你看到了？\N{\rEng}Ah, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.49,0:54:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利带他回来了！\N{\rEng}Centauri brought him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.06,0:54:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的，我看见了  -别说话\N{\rEng}Yes, I see. Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.76,0:54:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把我的钱拿回去了吗，亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}Does he have my money, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.80,0:54:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一大笔钱给你，森特利\N{\rEng}I have a fortune for you, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.73,0:54:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要坚持住\N{\rEng}Now, please be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.78,0:54:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱在这儿，全在这儿  一叠一叠的钱\N{\rEng}{\i1}It's here. It's all here. Piles and piles of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.02,0:54:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的\N{\rEng}All for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.28,0:54:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…\N{\rEng}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.85,0:54:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于\N{\rEng}At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.56,0:55:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，我要你知道，能把你带回来是最幸运的事\N{\rEng}Alex, I want you know, it was for the greatest good I brought you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.70,0:55:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，想…\N{\rEng}Of course, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.74,0:55:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要有钱也要付出点代价\N{\rEng}It never hurts to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.99,0:55:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好，老朋友\N{\rEng}Until the next dimension, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.60,0:55:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.00,0:55:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利？\N{\rEng}Centauri?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.01,0:55:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利？\N{\rEng}Centauri?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.05,0:55:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边境任何时候都有可能瓦解\N{\rEng}The Frontier could collapse at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.72,0:55:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.77,0:56:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的耳朵需要次手术  几乎听不到声音了\N{\rEng}{\i1}Now I need an earjob. Dying here. Dying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.39,0:57:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，究竟发生了什么？\N{\rEng}Alex, what the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.13,0:57:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯，你正在做恶梦\N{\rEng}Louis, you're having a terrible nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.14,0:57:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回去睡觉\N{\rEng}Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.95,0:57:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯！\N{\rEng}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.99,0:57:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，不\N{\rEng}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.68,0:57:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知，你家里有个替身在顶替你？\N{\rEng}Am I to understand there's a beta unit taking your place back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在努力尝试\N{\rEng}He's trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.35,0:57:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们完全可以推断，祖尔认为你还在地球上\N{\rEng}So it's safe to assume that Xur thinks you're still on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.52,0:57:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.39,0:57:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们在理论上可以算是有优势了\N{\rEng}That could work to our advantage, theoretically.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.13,0:58:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你现在看上去像个人了！\N{\rEng}Ah! Now you look human!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.05,0:58:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的刚星？\N{\rEng}Is this my Gunstar?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.55,0:58:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个样品，和其他飞船有点区别\N{\rEng}This is a prototype, different from the other ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.09,0:58:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有更远的射程，更大的威力…\N{\rEng}She has a greater range, more power,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.96,0:58:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时，也作了轻微的装备改良\N{\rEng}and a slight weapons modification.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.29,0:58:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，她还有防护层\N{\rEng}And, of course, she's got deflective plating,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.06,0:58:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她经得起几次直接攻击\N{\rEng}so she can withstand several direct hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.87,0:58:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是从这里，为飞船导航\N{\rEng}From here, this is where I navigate the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.14,0:58:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维护维生系统和推进系统\N{\rEng}maintain life support and propulsion systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.55,0:58:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我坐在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Okay. Where do I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.89,0:58:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那边，发射席上\N{\rEng}Way up there, in the gunnery chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.66,0:58:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站稳了！\N{\rEng}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.96,0:58:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.23,0:58:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，爬到发射席上\N{\rEng}Now, climb into the gunnery chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.24,0:58:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将你设置为发射状态\N{\rEng}Now, I'm moving you into launch position.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.41,0:58:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你前面有两个开关…\N{\rEng}There in front of you are the two switches
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.31,0:58:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以打开显示器  现在打开它们\N{\rEng}for your heads-up display. Turn them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.13,0:59:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你和敌人交战时…\N{\rEng}While you're engaging the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.40,0:59:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显示器会向你显示所有接近你的战舰\N{\rEng}the screen will reflect all battle instruments towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.97,0:59:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，它哪儿去了？\N{\rEng}Hey, where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.04,0:59:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它还在那儿，飘浮在氖气雾霭中\N{\rEng}It's still there, suspended in a xenon mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.70,0:59:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要以正确的角度看就能看到\N{\rEng}But it's only visible if you look dead ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.71,0:59:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，看到了\N{\rEng}Ah. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.84,0:59:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你左面的操纵杆是操纵你的座椅的\N{\rEng}The lever on your left is the chair controller.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.88,0:59:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以看到，所有的枪都跟着你一起移动\N{\rEng}As you can see, all guns will track with your every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.93,0:59:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右手抓紧瞄准器\N{\rEng}Grasp the target control with your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.14,0:59:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指可以操纵所有机枪——激光枪、霹雳弹…\N{\rEng}At your fingers is the weaponry, the lasers, photon bolts...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.77,0:59:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有粒子射线\N{\rEng}Photon bolts and the particle beams.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.01,0:59:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，这和我在家玩的一样啊\N{\rEng}Wait a minute. This is just like back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.28,0:59:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是什么？  -当心，当心…\N{\rEng}What's this? Careful, careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.74,0:59:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是死亡霸王花，最后关头才能用\N{\rEng}that's Death Blossom, a weapon of last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.11,0:59:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是，我不小心触动它的时候飞机库正在上升\N{\rEng}Luckily, I was in here working on it when the hangar went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.35,0:59:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？所有系统，开启！\N{\rEng}Now, are you ready? All systems, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.52,0:59:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点火！\N{\rEng}Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.80,0:59:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞机库什么时候上升？\N{\rEng}When did the hangar go up?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.74,1:00:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了，当祖尔袭击我们的时候！\N{\rEng}I told you, when Xur attacked.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.84,1:00:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那星空战士都在哪儿？\N{\rEng}And where were the Starfighters?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.11,1:00:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飞机库里！\N{\rEng}In the hangar!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.31,1:00:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说他们都死了？\N{\rEng}You mean they're dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.08,1:00:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死是个消极的概念\N{\rEng}Death is a primitive concept.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.15,1:00:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可认为他们在另一空间与邪恶而战\N{\rEng}I prefer to think of them as battling evil in another dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.02,1:00:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在另一空间？有多少人离开了？\N{\rEng}In another dimension? How many are left?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.79,1:00:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括你自己？\N{\rEng}Including yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.49,1:00:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.00,1:00:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个！\N{\rEng}One!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.34,1:00:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个？\N{\rEng}One?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.69,1:00:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！\N{\rEng}Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.82,1:00:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有舰队，没有星空战士，连个计划也没有？\N{\rEng}There's no fleet, no Starfighters, no plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.69,1:00:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-一艘飞船，你，我，没了？  -完全正确！\N{\rEng}One ship, you, me, and that's it? Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.13,1:00:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔认为你还在地球上\N{\rEng}Xur thinks you're still on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.33,1:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经典战略：突袭\N{\rEng}Classic military strategy. Surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.54,1:00:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那简直是送死！\N{\rEng}It'll be a slaughter!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.81,1:00:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要的就是这种精神！\N{\rEng}That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.28,1:00:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我去送死！\N{\rEng}No, my slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.78,1:00:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一艘飞船对抗整个部队？\N{\rEng}One ship against the whole Armada?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.78,1:00:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  一架刚星对抗整个部队！\N{\rEng}Yes. One Gunstar against the Armada.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.22,1:01:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是想和不可思议的敌人来一场破釜沉舟的战斗！\N{\rEng}I've always wanted to fight a desperate battle against incredible odds.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.79,1:01:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索目标，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Target lights, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.09,1:01:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索目标？\N{\rEng}Target lights?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.30,1:01:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你总得在还有机会的时候…\N{\rEng}Yes. You might want to squeeze off
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.10,1:01:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多打它几个回合吧？\N{\rEng}a few rounds while you have the chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.83,1:01:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发挥飞船的最大攻击力\N{\rEng}Just work the bugs out of the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.93,1:01:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟，这是她的处女航\N{\rEng}After all, it is her maiden voyage.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.53,1:01:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住，别和座椅过不去\N{\rEng}Steady. Don't fight the chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.77,1:01:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来  用枪瞄准\N{\rEng}Take your time. Watch your gun sights.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.71,1:01:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好目标\N{\rEng}Lead your targets.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.61,1:01:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之，放松就是了！\N{\rEng}And above all, relax!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.51,1:01:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好，我就要被杀得片甲不留…\N{\rEng}Terrific. I'm about to get killed a million miles from nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.76,1:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还有一个蜥蜴人叫我“放松”！\N{\rEng}with a gung-ho iguana who tells me, "Relax."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.90,1:01:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星空战士！\N{\rEng}Interstellar!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.24,1:02:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.14,1:02:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\rEng}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.98,1:02:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，来，慢慢举起来\N{\rEng}Okay, now, come on. Ease it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.75,1:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.72,1:02:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，行…行了！简单\N{\rEng}Oh, that's... That's it. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.90,1:02:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮又简单\N{\rEng}Nice and easy. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.44,1:02:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过来点就能装好了\N{\rEng}A little bit more and we'll get it in there, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.97,1:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.91,1:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  嗨，玛姬\N{\rEng}Sorry. Hi, Maggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.88,1:03:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，你没事吧？\N{\rEng}Alex, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.15,1:03:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊  我…没事\N{\rEng}Yeah. Yeah, I'm... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.92,1:03:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，再来一次\N{\rEng}Come on. Try it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.92,1:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闻到什么了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you smell anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.47,1:03:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEng}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.67,1:03:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像…\N{\rEng}Like a Z...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.87,1:03:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了\N{\rEng}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.18,1:03:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想为昨天晚上给你的巴掌道歉\N{\rEng}I just wanted to say I'm sorry for slapping you last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.15,1:03:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，没关系，玛姬  我活该\N{\rEng}Oh, that's okay, Maggs. I deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.02,1:03:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.96,1:03:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不…我们今晚去银湖弥补一下？\N{\rEng}Well, maybe we can make it up to each other tonight at Silver Lake?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.34,1:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军将会从这里进入边境\N{\rEng}The Armada will break through the Frontier here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.88,1:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十公里后到达赖罗斯\N{\rEng}and reach Rylos in 20 klicks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.38,1:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲板上的空中部队将跟随母舰\N{\rEng}Squadrons of deck fighters will precede the mother ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.22,1:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空中部队？有多少空中部队？\N{\rEng}Squadrons? How many squadrons?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.12,1:04:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数量我倒不在乎\N{\rEng}It isn't the number of squadrons that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.42,1:04:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座通信塔将指令…\N{\rEng}It's this communication turret that sends out
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.36,1:04:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发送给空中部队\N{\rEng}the commands to the deck fighters,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.96,1:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样，他们就能同时作战\N{\rEng}which enables them to act as one during the fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.26,1:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，我们摧毁塔台以破坏空中部队\N{\rEng}Wait a second. We knock out the turret to get the fighters.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.03,1:04:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要摧毁塔台，我们就要穿过空中部队？\N{\rEng}But to get the turret, we have to get through the fighters.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.64,1:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就死了\N{\rEng}We're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.07,1:04:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在到达边境前我会想出办法的\N{\rEng}I'll have it all figured out by the time we reach the Frontier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.05,1:04:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\rEng}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.29,1:04:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是边境\N{\rEng}The Frontier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.70,1:04:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪，运输舰…\N{\rEng}Now, that's strange. What's a cargo ship
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.80,1:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在边境附近干什么？\N{\rEng}doing this close to the Frontier?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.50,1:04:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，这里是刚星一号\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hail. This is Gunstar One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.91,1:05:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复，这里是刚星一号\N{\rEng}{\i1}I repeat, this is Gunstar One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.81,1:05:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请确认身份\N{\rEng}{\i1}Identify yourself, please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.23,1:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，当心！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex, look out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.93,1:05:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祖尔的飞船！\N{\rEng}A Xurian ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.07,1:05:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Congratulations, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.30,1:05:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一个活体目标\N{\rEng}This is your first live target.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.21,1:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活体？\N{\rEng}Live?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.11,1:05:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五公里后进入射程  准备！\N{\rEng}Within range in five klicks. Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.73,1:05:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拦截了他的信号\N{\rEng}I've blocked its beam of frequency,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.46,1:05:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他没办法向总部报告\N{\rEng}so it can't report back to the Armada.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.93,1:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-准备好了就开火！  -格里格，等等！\N{\rEng}Fire when ready! Grig, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.58,1:05:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能在洞穴里跟丢了，亚里克斯！开火！\N{\rEng}We mustn't lose them in these caves, Alex! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.65,1:06:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Shoot, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.69,1:06:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火！\N{\rEng}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.21,1:06:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你成功了！\N{\rEng}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.42,1:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了？是你成功了！\N{\rEng}I did it? You did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.05,1:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你差点让我送了命！\N{\rEng}You almost got me killed!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.56,1:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最诚意的道歉，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}My deepest apologies, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.49,1:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本打算让你经历了枪林弹雨以后…\N{\rEng}I had hoped that by putting you in the thick of battle,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.93,1:06:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个伟大的星空战士即将诞生\N{\rEng}a great Starfighter would emerge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.53,1:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，唉  也许你本来就不是这块料\N{\rEng}But, alas. Perhaps there was never one within you to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.42,1:07:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我载你回家吧\N{\rEng}I shall take you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.55,1:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿，你仍可以过上很长一段时间的安稳日子…\N{\rEng}You still may live a long and fruitful life back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.79,1:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到柯-旦打到地球\N{\rEng}That is, until the Ko-Dan reach Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.46,1:07:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但到了那个时候…\N{\rEng}But then again...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.59,1:07:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，布雷克！让那破音响再响一点啊！\N{\rEng}Hey, yo, Blake! Make that sucker blast, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.79,1:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题，伙计！\N{\rEng}You got it, dude! All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.63,1:07:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克回来是拿他的裤子的对吧？\N{\rEng}So Blake comes back in to grab his pants, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.33,1:07:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到她奶奶，说…\N{\rEng}Sees her old lady, and says,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.17,1:07:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“希望这不会让我星期二晚上没饭吃”\N{\rEng}"I hope this doesn't rule out dinner on Tuesday night."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.04,1:07:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真搞笑！\N{\rEng}That's my man!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.42,1:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，你没事吧？\N{\rEng}Alex, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.09,1:08:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？\N{\rEng}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.19,1:08:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，没事  怎么了？\N{\rEng}Yeah, sure. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.50,1:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，你老是走神\N{\rEng}I don't know. You're just acting spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.67,1:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这很不像你啊\N{\rEng}You're... You're not yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.10,1:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是我，你现在会怎么办？\N{\rEng}Well, if you were me, what would you be doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.91,1:08:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先呢，我会先好好享受生活\N{\rEng}Well, for one thing, I'd be trying to enjoy myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.43,1:08:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠在车上，开开玩笑，大笑\N{\rEng}Leaning back. Kidding around. Laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.43,1:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笑？\N{\rEng}Laughing?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.70,1:08:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个开始，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Well, it's a start, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.97,1:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笑\N{\rEng}Laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.56,1:09:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好地方  让我想起我的家\N{\rEng}Nice place. Reminds me of home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.54,1:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这能让你想家？\N{\rEng}This reminds you of home?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.41,1:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，是啊\N{\rEng}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.25,1:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我的妻子和六千个孩子住在地下\N{\rEng}I live below ground with my wifeoid and 6,000 little Griglings.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.63,1:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少，在祖尔把他们变成努力之前\N{\rEng}At least, until Xur turns them into slaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.18,1:09:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这个物种住在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where does your kind live?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.58,1:10:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，基本上都住在房子里\N{\rEng}Oh, uh, houses, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.62,1:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是地上的洞穴  看看这个\N{\rEng}That's caves above ground. See, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.85,1:10:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我全家\N{\rEng}Here's my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.19,1:10:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，这是…\N{\rEng}See, that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.29,1:10:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我父母，这是我弟弟，路易斯，这是玛姬\N{\rEng}That's my folks and my brother, Louis, and that's Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.57,1:10:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们住在移动的家里\N{\rEng}Uh, we live in a mobile home.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.48,1:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是会去各种地方的洞穴\N{\rEng}That's a cave that goes places.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.18,1:10:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们从来没去过别的地方\N{\rEng}Only we never went anyplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.99,1:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个从来不去别处的移动洞穴  有意思\N{\rEng}A mobile cave that never went anywhere. Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.19,1:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，但是我们在拖车场附近也有底下的洞穴\N{\rEng}Yeah, but we have below-ground caves near the trailer parks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.66,1:10:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我弟弟路易斯过去常常在里面玩捉迷藏…\N{\rEng}Me and my brother, Louis, used to play hide-and-seek in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.20,1:10:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏\N{\rEng}Hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.27,1:10:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏是什么，亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}What is it, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.34,1:10:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想，也许我们可以躲在这里…\N{\rEng}Well, I was just thinking, maybe we could hide here,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.05,1:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等敌军经过的时候，从后方攻击他们的塔台\N{\rEng}let the Armada pass by, and then hit the turret from behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.46,1:10:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，我们就以突袭的方式打败他们\N{\rEng}Then we might take them by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.20,1:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的策略也许真能奏效\N{\rEng}Your plan might really have worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.50,1:11:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜没有星空战士来执行它了\N{\rEng}What a pity there are no Starfighters left to carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.47,1:11:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.86,1:11:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个祖尔的基地！\N{\rEng}A Xurian base!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.94,1:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正前方还有两个  快速靠近中！\N{\rEng}Two more dead ahead! Closing fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.01,1:12:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往地球的航线已准备完毕\N{\rEng}Earth course is logged into navigational beams.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.89,1:12:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格里格？\N{\rEng}Grig?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.79,1:12:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事，亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}What is it, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.30,1:12:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的只剩下一个星空战士了\N{\rEng}Maybe there is a Starfighter left.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.72,1:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Ow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.80,1:13:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\rEng}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.13,1:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是不是该把我的舌头伸到你耳朵里？\N{\rEng}Should I put my tongue in your ear now?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.21,1:13:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Don't bother, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.51,1:13:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…\N{\rEng}Well, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.68,1:13:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不习惯这种事…\N{\rEng}I'm kind of new at these gland games.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.02,1:13:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说些什么啊？\N{\rEng}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.05,1:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像你是从外太空来的，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}It's like you're a million miles away, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.70,1:13:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂，喂，等等啊，宝贝儿\N{\rEng}{\i1}Whoa, whoa, whoa. Wait. Darling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.37,1:13:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝儿，原谅我吧\N{\rEng}{\i1}Darling, forgive me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.76,1:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“宝贝儿，原谅我吧”\N{\rEng}{\i1}"Darling, forgive me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.83,1:13:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.23,1:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的茱丽叶，我的维纳斯\N{\rEng}{\i1}You're my Juliet. My Venus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.71,1:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你是我的茱丽叶，我的维纳斯”\N{\rEng}"You're my Juliet. My Venus."
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.89,1:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.43,1:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他女孩儿对我来说都毫无意义\N{\rEng}{\i1}All the other girls meant nothing to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.03,1:14:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱的是你啊  你，你\N{\rEng}{\i1}It was you, you, you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.23,1:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口，跟我说点脏的\N{\rEng}{\i1}Shut up and talk dirty to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.27,1:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“其他女孩儿对我来说都毫无意义  我爱的是你啊  你，你”\N{\rEng}"The other girls meant nothing to me. It was you, you..."
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.28,1:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你说点脏的吗？\N{\rEng}Should I talk dirty to you now?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.11,1:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\rEng}That does it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.51,1:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，天啊  好的，我放弃了\N{\rEng}Oh, God. All right. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.13,1:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是亚里克斯罗根\N{\rEng}I'm not Alex Rogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.66,1:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.23,1:14:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个替身\N{\rEng}I'm a beta unit.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.43,1:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是亚里克斯的复制品\N{\rEng}I'm an exact duplicate of Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.97,1:14:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那儿拯救全宇宙…\N{\rEng}He's up there saving the universe,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.20,1:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿做敌军的诱饵\N{\rEng}while I'm down here for target practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.74,1:14:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧？\N{\rEng}See?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.81,1:15:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！或者不管你是谁，等等，等等\N{\rEng}Alex! Or whatever you are. Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.82,1:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？让我走\N{\rEng}What are you do... Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.92,1:15:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个赞多-赞向总部报告…\N{\rEng}If that Zando-Zan reports back
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.99,1:15:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说我不是亚里克斯，亚里克斯就有危险了\N{\rEng}that I'm not Alex, Alex is in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.20,1:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你呆在这儿  -不，我不要\N{\rEng}You're staying here. No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.53,1:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪儿都不要呆直到我弄清楚真相\N{\rEng}I'm not staying anywhere until I find out what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.57,1:15:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，我的卡车！嘿，嘿，回来！\N{\rEng}Hey, my truck! Hey, hey, come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.71,1:15:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一点点擦坏，你就死定了，罗根！\N{\rEng}Scratch that paint, and you're dead, Rogan!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.26,1:15:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵已就绪，指挥长\N{\rEng}Ready to invade, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.79,1:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵\N{\rEng}Invade.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.89,1:15:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥长，祖尔飞船一直没有回复我们的入侵代码\N{\rEng}Commander, the Xurian ships have not answered our invasion code.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.07,1:15:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边境瓦解了，月亮消失了…\N{\rEng}The Frontier is down, the moon is eclipsed,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.51,1:15:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星空战士都死了  开始入侵吧！\N{\rEng}the Starfighters are dead. lnvade!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.78,1:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有空中部队，半速前进  开启能源探测器\N{\rEng}All squadrons ahead, half speed, with energy probes on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.29,1:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源探测器  快关闭，亚里克斯  关闭\N{\rEng}Energy probe. Shut down, Alex. Shut down.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.36,1:16:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关闭\N{\rEng}Power off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.42,1:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯在太空中？\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex? ln space?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.32,1:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的假的？  -真的！我不是一直在跟你说嘛\N{\rEng}Is this for real? - Yes! That's what I'm trying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.96,1:16:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是真的！\N{\rEng}{\i1}It's all for real!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.26,1:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那别说话了，开车啊！\N{\rEng}Well, then, don't talk. Drive!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.12,1:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里尔指挥长，紧急频率收到信号\N{\rEng}Commander Kril, we're getting a signal on the alert frequency.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.32,1:17:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接收\N{\rEng}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.23,1:17:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了  好的\N{\rEng}There it is. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.83,1:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我接近发射器以后你就跳，知道了吗？\N{\rEng}Now, when I give the signal, we're gonna jump! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.80,1:17:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-“跳”是什么意思？  -我们用车撞掉它\N{\rEng}What do you mean, "Jump"? We're gonna ram him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.73,1:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.84,1:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灭绝特使六号有一则消息\N{\rEng}Extermination Emissary Zeta 6, one message.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.54,1:17:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？跳！\N{\rEng}Ready? Jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.51,1:17:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.54,1:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“最后的星空战士…”\N{\rEng}"The last Starfighter..."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.46,1:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我一个人情，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}You owe me one, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.70,1:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.57,1:17:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通讯中断，指挥长\N{\rEng}Transmission pulsars have stopped, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.91,1:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的星空战士…\N{\rEng}The last Starfighter...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.81,1:17:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已死亡！\N{\rEng}Is dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.58,1:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的星空战士已死亡！\N{\rEng}The last Starfighter is dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.81,1:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是无可阻挡的了！全速前进！\N{\rEng}Nothing can stop us now. Ahead full.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.55,1:17:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往赖罗斯！\N{\rEng}To Rylos!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.61,1:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥舰！\N{\rEng}The command ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.92,1:18:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那儿！塔台在最后面\N{\rEng}There! The turret at the far end!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.17,1:18:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了\N{\rEng}I see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.57,1:18:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运，星空战士\N{\rEng}Good luck, Starfighter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.68,1:18:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你所做的一切，格里格\N{\rEng}Thanks, Grig. For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.59,1:18:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你，亚里克斯罗根\N{\rEng}I love you, Alex Rogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.99,1:18:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六\N{\rEng}Six.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.54,1:18:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显示器，开启\N{\rEng}Heads-up display. Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.74,1:18:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五\N{\rEng}Five.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.88,1:18:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激光枪，开启\N{\rEng}Lasers. Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.78,1:19:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-四  -粒子枪，开启\N{\rEng}Four. Particle beam. Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.48,1:19:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-三  -霹雳弹，开启\N{\rEng}Three. Proton bolts. Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.25,1:19:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-二  -座椅控制，开启\N{\rEng}Two. Chair control. Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.78,1:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一\N{\rEng}One.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.15,1:19:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\rEng}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.60,1:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪警报\N{\rEng}{\i1}Tracking alert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.28,1:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不明飞船  到底是什么？\N{\rEng}{\i1}Unidentified craft. What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.69,1:19:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEng}{\i1}Wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.26,1:19:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚星！\N{\rEng}Gunstar!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.19,1:19:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的星空战士不是死了吗？\N{\rEng}So, the last Starfighter is dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.56,1:19:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了  抓起来！\N{\rEng}This has gone far enough. Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.80,1:19:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们敢！我是赖罗斯的帝王！\N{\rEng}How dare you? I am the Emperor of Rylos!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.48,1:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我，只有我，才能指挥这…\N{\rEng}I and I alone command this entire op...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.48,1:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！我命令你！\N{\rEng}Release me! I command you!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.12,1:19:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会付出生命的代价的！\N{\rEng}You will pay for this with your lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.96,1:20:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全面开火！\N{\rEng}All guns fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.47,1:20:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿，塔台！\N{\rEng}There it is, the turret!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.91,1:20:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，就现在！\N{\rEng}Alex, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.51,1:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.62,1:20:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击中了！\N{\rEng}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.26,1:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，亚里克斯！开火！\N{\rEng}Hurry, Alex! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.49,1:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军积聚已经到达了赖罗斯！\N{\rEng}The Armada's almost to Rylos!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.25,1:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}逃生通道开启{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Escape pod activated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.36,1:20:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}逃生通道开启{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Escape pod ignition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.13,1:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的感应器探测不到刚星了\N{\rEng}The Gunstar is gone from our sensors.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.06,1:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向指挥部发出警报\N{\rEng}Alert wing commanders.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.53,1:20:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通信塔台已被摧毁\N{\rEng}{\i1}Communication turret is destroyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.91,1:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的通信雷达系统都瘫痪了，指挥部\N{\rEng}{\i1}All communication radar systems are out, Wing Commander.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.01,1:21:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成视觉攻击队列\N{\rEng}{\i1}Proceed with a visual attack formation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.45,1:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维生系统良好  弹药装备量满\N{\rEng}Life support good. Ammo packs at peak.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.47,1:21:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我们要使用死亡霸王花了\N{\rEng}I think we've got to use Death Blossom.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.27,1:21:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住，死亡霸王花只能在近距离…\N{\rEng}Remember, Death Blossom delivers
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.94,1:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给目标以重击\N{\rEng}only one massive volley at close range.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.94,1:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理论上是这样的\N{\rEng}Theoretically.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.44,1:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“理论上”是什么意思？\N{\rEng}What do you mean, "Theoretically"?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.91,1:21:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟，死亡霸王花从来没被测试过\N{\rEng}After all, D.B. has never been tested.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.08,1:21:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它也许会让飞船超负荷，而毁了飞船\N{\rEng}It might overload the systems. Blow up the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.81,1:21:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在担心什么，格里格？\N{\rEng}What are you worried about, Grig?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.98,1:21:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理论上，我们已经死了\N{\rEng}Theoretically, we should already be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.92,1:21:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开死亡霸王花踏板，开启\N{\rEng}Open Death Blossom petals. Switch is on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.21,1:21:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没进入射程千万别发动死亡霸王花\N{\rEng}Do not trigger D.B. until we're within range.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.98,1:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先用激光攻击，直到我收到信号\N{\rEng}Just use your lasers until I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.68,1:22:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得要…\N{\rEng}Remember to lead...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.82,1:22:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被星际联盟录取…\N{\rEng}I've been recruited by the Star League
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.32,1:22:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防御边境\N{\rEng}to defend the Frontier.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.09,1:22:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？\N{\rEng}Now, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.19,1:22:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候了  我们开始吧\N{\rEng}This is it. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.96,1:22:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊！\N{\rEng}Charge!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.10,1:22:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右面！\N{\rEng}On your right!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.18,1:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左面！\N{\rEng}Your left!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.82,1:22:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪躲！\N{\rEng}Evade!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.02,1:22:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量储备不足！我们需要时间充电！\N{\rEng}Power packs are low! We need time to recharge!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.76,1:22:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激光能量耗尽\N{\rEng}Laser power draining!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.10,1:23:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格里格，我的武器都用完了  使用霸王花吗？\N{\rEng}Grig, my weapons are gone! Should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.37,1:23:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着，慢着\N{\rEng}Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.44,1:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到他们都在霸王花的射程内\N{\rEng}Wait till they're all in Death Blossom range!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.00,1:23:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射！\N{\rEng}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.74,1:23:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们成功了！\N{\rEng}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.94,1:24:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我们真的成功了，对吧？\N{\rEng}Yes, we actually did, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.81,1:24:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指挥舰！\N{\rEng}{\i1}The command ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.88,1:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥长，我们的枪已损坏\N{\rEng}Commander, our guns are out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.40,1:24:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维修小组正在维修\N{\rEng}Damage control is repairing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.13,1:24:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要什么枪！急速前进！\N{\rEng}Forget the guns! Ramming speed!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.41,1:24:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格里格，我们需要能量！\N{\rEng}Grig, we need power!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.54,1:24:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡霸王花用尽了所有的能量\N{\rEng}Death Blossom's drained all power.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.61,1:24:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在尽力，我要运行能量激增模式！\N{\rEng}I'm working on it. I'm trying to run boost.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.79,1:24:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们剩下的只是维生系统的能量\N{\rEng}All we have left is life support power!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.27,1:24:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格里格！\N{\rEng}Grig!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.78,1:24:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了！\N{\rEng}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.72,1:25:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以开火了  我们有能量了  开火！开火！\N{\rEng}Weapons on! We have them now! Fire. Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.43,1:25:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估损报告\N{\rEng}Damage report!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.79,1:25:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导航系统瘫痪，转向系统瘫痪\N{\rEng}Guidance system out. Auxiliary steering out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.36,1:25:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！\N{\rEng}Divert!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.78,1:25:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！\N{\rEng}Divert!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.21,1:25:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转向系统无响应\N{\rEng}She won't answer the helm!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.71,1:25:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被锁定在月球的重力轨道上\N{\rEng}We're locked into the moon's gravitational pull!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.15,1:25:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要怎么办？\N{\rEng}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.52,1:25:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有死路一条\N{\rEng}We die.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.15,1:26:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表星际联盟和所有的赖罗斯公民…\N{\rEng}{\i1}On behalf of the Star League and all citizens of Rylos,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.69,1:26:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祝贺你光荣凯旋\N{\rEng}I congratulate you on your dazzling victory.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.96,1:26:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢你  -谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.63,1:26:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你知道，边境已经瓦解…\N{\rEng}But as you know, the Frontier is down,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.07,1:26:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖尔也逃跑了  危险依然存在\N{\rEng}Xur escaped, and there is still danger.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.60,1:26:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我在想，你是不是愿意呆在这儿…\N{\rEng}So I was wondering if you wouldn't be willing to stay on,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.80,1:26:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重建星际联盟？\N{\rEng}and rebuild the Starfighter Legion.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.34,1:26:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.69,1:26:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重建星际联盟？\N{\rEng}Rebuild the Legion?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.35,1:26:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.06,1:26:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，你也会有一位老朋友来帮忙\N{\rEng}Of course, you'd have the help of an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.63,1:26:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老朋友？谁？\N{\rEng}An old friend? Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.55,1:26:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森特利！我以为你死了！\N{\rEng}Centauri! I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.46,1:27:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我死了，还错过精彩的战事？哦，不！\N{\rEng}Me die and miss all the excitement? Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.03,1:27:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是进入休眠状态好让我的身体自行恢复\N{\rEng}I was merely dormant while my body repaired itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.66,1:27:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就废话少说了\N{\rEng}Now, I won't bore you with details.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.70,1:27:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一句话：你在赖罗斯星，我的孩子\N{\rEng}Suffice it to say, you're on Rylos, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.57,1:27:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想着人类了\N{\rEng}Stop thinking human.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.04,1:27:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一课\N{\rEng}That's lesson number one.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.64,1:27:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，第二课，你在这里远近闻名\N{\rEng}Now, lesson number two, you've got a good thing going here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.14,1:27:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持微笑，别扫兴\N{\rEng}Keep smiling. Don't blow it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.98,1:27:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三课，总是相信森特利\N{\rEng}Lesson number three, always trust Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.63,1:27:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，他们多爱你！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex, they love you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.57,1:27:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，整个赖罗斯星就在你下面\N{\rEng}You see, all Rylos is behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.97,1:27:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得留下 ，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}You've got to stay, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.64,1:27:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会留下的，对吧？\N{\rEng}You will stay, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.68,1:27:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，他会留下的\N{\rEng}{\i1}Of course, he'll stay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.45,1:27:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真的很令人欣慰，森特利\N{\rEng}That's very reassuring, Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.65,1:27:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格里格，我就把这些事交给你了\N{\rEng}Grig, I leave it in your capable hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.15,1:27:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留下\N{\rEng}I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.31,1:28:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}亚里克斯！亚里克斯！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex! Alex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.03,1:28:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好…\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.84,1:28:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，星空战士\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.58,1:28:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，你看到亚里克斯了吗？\N{\rEng}Bunny, have you seen Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.04,1:28:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢\N{\rEng}Can't say that I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.45,1:28:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问玛姬吧，她知道他在哪儿\N{\rEng}Well, ask Maggie. She knows where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.75,1:28:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她原本和他在一起的\N{\rEng}She was with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.75,1:28:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬，亚里克斯呢？\N{\rEng}Maggie, where's Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.22,1:28:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的卡车在哪儿？你的男朋友在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Yeah, where's my truck? Where's your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.89,1:28:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗根太太，关于亚里克斯，他…\N{\rEng}Mrs. Rogan, about Alex, you see, he's...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.79,1:28:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么东西？发生什么了？  -我不知道\N{\rEng}What is it? What's going on? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.26,1:29:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，天啊！\N{\rEng}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.87,1:29:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，我们被侵略了！\N{\rEng}All right! We're being invaded!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.64,1:29:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬\N{\rEng}Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.04,1:29:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬\N{\rEng}Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.64,1:30:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.90,1:30:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，玛姬\N{\rEng}Hi, Maggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.11,1:30:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Alex,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.34,1:30:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗？\N{\rEng}is it you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.44,1:31:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你吗？\N{\rEng}I mean, is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.25,1:31:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看！\N{\rEng}Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.12,1:31:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊！\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.16,1:31:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你！\N{\rEng}It is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.03,1:31:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚里克斯！亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}It's Alex! Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.57,1:31:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，发生了什么？\N{\rEng}Alex, what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.21,1:31:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\rEng}What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.18,1:31:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的太空飞船？\N{\rEng}Is this your spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.68,1:31:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他中了什么邪了\N{\rEng}I don't know what's gotten into him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.49,1:31:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真搞不懂\N{\rEng}I don't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.25,1:31:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太奇怪了！\N{\rEng}It's so strange!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.79,1:31:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，等等  大家，安静\N{\rEng}Wait. Hold it. Hold it, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.29,1:31:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，这一切是怎么回事？\N{\rEng}Alex, what is all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.80,1:31:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了另外一个星球，妈\N{\rEng}I've been to another planet, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.94,1:31:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外一个星球？\N{\rEng}Another planet?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.21,1:31:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁帮我修好了天线？\N{\rEng}Who was it helped fix my antenna?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.41,1:31:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，谁偷了我的卡车？\N{\rEng}Yeah, who stole my truck?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.48,1:31:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁切断了我家的电？\N{\rEng}And cut my electric?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.55,1:31:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还把我的炉子弄坏了\N{\rEng}And ruined my stove?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.65,1:31:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，那是…那是个替身\N{\rEng}Oh, that was... That was a beta unit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.99,1:31:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替身？\N{\rEng}{\i1}Beta unit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.12,1:31:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个机器人\N{\rEng}A robot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.19,1:31:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机器人？什么…\N{\rEng}Robot? What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.59,1:31:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托！\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.89,1:31:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽！\N{\rEng}A monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.46,1:32:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽\N{\rEng}A monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.00,1:32:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他给他们套上了链子\N{\rEng}{\i1}He got them chains on him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.10,1:32:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，是外星人！\N{\rEng}All right! It's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.17,1:32:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，不，等等！嘿，嘿！\N{\rEng}Oh, no, wait! Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.78,1:32:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶，把枪放下  你们怎么回事啊？\N{\rEng}Granny, put away that shotgun. What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.88,1:32:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的朋友格里格\N{\rEng}This is my friend Grig.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.35,1:32:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你们大家见见我的朋友\N{\rEng}I want you all to meet my friend here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.79,1:32:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在开玩笑吧！\N{\rEng}{\i1}You got to be kidding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.85,1:32:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格里格，这是布恩太太\N{\rEng}Grig, this is Mrs. Boone.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.99,1:32:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.09,1:32:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.23,1:32:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是艾尔维拉\N{\rEng}And this is Elvira.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.46,1:32:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兴会\N{\rEng}Delighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.60,1:32:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  你好吗？\N{\rEng}Me, too. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.03,1:32:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\rEng}I do well.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.30,1:32:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是奶奶\N{\rEng}And this is Granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.67,1:32:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兴会\N{\rEng}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.10,1:32:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兴会\N{\rEng}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.94,1:32:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是Otis\N{\rEng}And this here's Otis.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.47,1:32:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你\N{\rEng}A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.94,1:32:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯的任何朋友都…\N{\rEng}Any friend of Alex...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.39,1:32:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是玛姬\N{\rEng}And this is Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.39,1:32:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常荣幸\N{\rEng}A very large pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.09,1:32:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.63,1:32:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是路易斯！\N{\rEng}You must be Louis!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.27,1:32:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情我如雷贯耳\N{\rEng}I hear good things about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.84,1:33:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗？我很有名\N{\rEng}Hear that, you slimes? I'm famous.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.88,1:33:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我的母亲\N{\rEng}And this is my mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.26,1:33:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该为亚里克斯骄傲，罗根太太\N{\rEng}You should be proud of Alex, Mrs. Rogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.60,1:33:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都应该为他骄傲\N{\rEng}You must all be proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.93,1:33:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拯救了星际联盟以及成百上千的世界，包括地球\N{\rEng}He saved the Star League and hundreds of worlds, including Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.83,1:33:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，你太棒了！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Oh, for heaven's sake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.77,1:33:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，天啊！\N{\rEng}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.41,1:33:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了，亚里克斯\N{\rEng}Time to leave, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.54,1:33:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.31,1:33:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得走，妈\N{\rEng}I have to, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.54,1:33:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们那儿需要我\N{\rEng}They need me up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.08,1:33:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，亚里克斯，我就知道有一天你要离开我们\N{\rEng}Oh, Alex, I always knew you'd leave someday,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.92,1:33:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没想到会是这样\N{\rEng}but I never expected this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.82,1:33:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能去吗，亚里克斯？行吗？\N{\rEng}Gee, can I go, too, Alex? Can I?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.10,1:33:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了，小子，那里只有足够的空间…\N{\rEng}Sorry, squirt. There's only enough room up there
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.80,1:33:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我，格里格和玛姬\N{\rEng}for me, Grig, and Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.14,1:33:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我？  -没错\N{\rEng}Me? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.37,1:33:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，我可不认为我能…\N{\rEng}Alex, I don't think I can...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.74,1:33:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？过来，过来\N{\rEng}What? Come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.05,1:33:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我还会回来吗？\N{\rEng}Why else do you think I came back?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.88,1:33:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…我们不是说了要永远在一起的吗？\N{\rEng}Well... Didn't we say we'd always be together?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.95,1:34:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，可是我是指在这里或者城里\N{\rEng}Well, yeah, I mean, together here or in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.99,1:34:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是，在那儿，亚里克斯…\N{\rEng}But... But up there, Alex...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.76,1:34:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬，你必须得来  你看，我不知道…\N{\rEng}Maggs, you got to come. You see, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.29,1:34:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我什么时候才回来\N{\rEng}I don't know when I'm gonna be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.37,1:34:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白吗？这，就是我们最大的机会了\N{\rEng}Don't you see? This is it. This is our big chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.27,1:34:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像Otis说的…\N{\rEng}It's like what Otis says,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.64,1:34:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当机会来临时…\N{\rEng}when it comes, you got to grab on
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.34,1:34:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手紧紧抓住它\N{\rEng}with both hands and hold tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.11,1:34:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，奶奶怎么办呢，亚里克斯？\N{\rEng}Well, what about Granny, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.52,1:34:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对，我是很害怕离开这里\N{\rEng}You're right. I'm scared of leaving here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.56,1:34:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就不能留下呢？\N{\rEng}Why can't you just stay?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.19,1:34:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬，我必须得走  我要你也跟我走\N{\rEng}Maggie, I have to leave, and I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.71,1:34:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！快啊！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex! Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.68,1:34:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了\N{\rEng}Well, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.06,1:34:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.00,1:34:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯，他们的雷达我们屏蔽不了多久了\N{\rEng}Alex, we can't hold off their radar any longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.60,1:35:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，来了  我要走了，妈\N{\rEng}Yeah, okay. I got to go, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.30,1:35:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再见  多保重  -再见，孩子\N{\rEng}Bye. Take it easy. Bye, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.71,1:35:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期  大家，后会有期了\N{\rEng}So long. So long, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.25,1:35:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bye, Alex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.45,1:35:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.78,1:35:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bye, Alex. Bye, Alex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.10,1:35:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}{\i1}Alex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.67,1:35:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…\N{\rEng}Granny...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.20,1:35:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得要写信告诉我们那边的情况\N{\rEng}Be sure and write, or whatever it is they do up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.82,1:35:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚里克斯！等等，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Alex! Wait, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.37,1:35:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来！快回来！\N{\rEng}Get back! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.71,1:35:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了！\N{\rEng}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.01,1:35:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持距离！注意安全！\N{\rEng}Keep your distance! Watch what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.66,1:36:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持距离！\N{\rEng}Keep your distance, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.59,1:36:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意打起仗来真带劲\N{\rEng}This baby really packs a punch!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.96,1:36:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.83,1:36:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.93,1:36:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他啊！再见！\N{\rEng}Look at him! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.53,1:36:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.80,1:36:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，走吧  他们在那儿会很快乐的  再见，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}Oh, go on. They're gonna be happy up there! So long, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.34,1:36:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期，亚里克斯！\N{\rEng}So long, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.35,1:36:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要出名了，对吧，Otis？\N{\rEng}We're gonna be famous, aren't we, Otis?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.86,1:36:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错！\N{\rEng}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.16,1:36:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界，全宇宙都将知道\N{\rEng}The whole world, the whole universe is gonna know about it!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.00,1:36:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星星闪耀的地方…\N{\rEng}Starlite, Starbrite,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.77,1:36:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是亚里克斯和玛姬出发去宇宙的地方！\N{\rEng}the place where Alex and Maggie left for the stars!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.44,1:36:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯！路易斯！\N{\rEng}Louis! Louis!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.81,1:36:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好，星空战士！{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Greetings, Starfighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.47,1:36:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你已被星空联盟录取…{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You have been recruited by the Star League{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.38,1:36:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}誓死保卫边境，抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵{\i0}\N{\rEng}{\i1}to defend the Frontier against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.72,1:36:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！\N{\rEng}Wow!


